cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single image dehazing using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) architecture, which falls under the category of machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of frequency information as additional priors, which falls under the category of signal processing, making cs.GR (Graphics) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with image synthesis and enhancement, which falls under the category of multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category as well.
